OL,3,CFamily of Jersey man who died in care
OL,4,Cof paramedics who broke the law speak
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThe family of a Jersey man who died of
OL,8,Fa cardiac arrest while in the care of
OL,9,Fparamedics has spoken out for the
OL,10,Ffirst time.
OL,12,F39 year old Frazer Irvine died in
OL,13,FMarch 2022, whilst in the care of
OL,14,Fparamedics Tom Le Sauteur, 36, and
OL,15,FJohn Sutherland, 61.
OL,17,FLe Sauteur and Sutherland were found
OL,18,Fguilty of failing to provide
OL,19,Freasonable care to a man in the
OL,20,Fmoments before his death.
