OL,4,Cof paramedics who broke the law speak
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FIn a statement, Mr Irvine's family
OL,8,Fsaid: "Frazer was a much-loved son,
OL,9,Fbrother, uncle and friend. The efforts
OL,10,Fto portray Frazer as a violent,
OL,11,Faggressive drunk could not be further
OL,12,Ffrom the truth.
OL,14,F"Anyone who viewed the CCTV that the
OL,15,Fparamedics obviously never realised
OL,16,Fwas recording, the subsequent evidence
OL,17,Ffrom body worn cameras and the
OL,18,Fevidence provided in court by
OL,19,Fwitnesses will be aware of the truth."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
