OL,3,CFamily of Jersey man who died in care
OL,4,Cof paramedics who broke the law speak
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThe family added: "The actions of the
OL,8,Fparamedics fell well below any
OL,9,Facceptable standards of care. Even the
OL,10,Fexpert hired by the defendants could
OL,11,Fnot defend their actions.
OL,13,F"The family are convinced, as are many
OL,14,Fothers, that if even basic first aid
OL,15,Fhad been administered, then Frazer may
OL,16,Fwell have survived.
