OL,4,Cof paramedics who broke the law speak
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"The authorities in Jersey do not
OL,8,Fbring cases lightly. They must decide
OL,9,Fthat there is both a reasonable
OL,10,Fprospect of conviction and that the
OL,11,Fprosecution is in the public interest.
OL,13,F"On 18 March 2022, Frazer reached out
OL,14,Ffor help but was tragically let down
OL,15,Fby those whose job it was to
OL,16,Fadminister that help. What is hard to
OL,17,Faccept is that those in a caring
OL,18,Fprofession could show such little
OL,19,Fregard for human life."
