OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FLe Sauteur and Sutherland have told
OL,8,FITV News they intend to appeal the
OL,9,Fdecision of Jurats.
OL,11,FAmbulance technician Tom Le Sauteur,
OL,12,F36, and paramedic John Sutherland, 61,
OL,13,Fwere sentenced at the Royal Court to
OL,14,Fpay #500 each in legal costs and
OL,15,Fissued a 'conditional discharge' for
OL,16,Ftwo years - which means they will not
OL,17,Fface punishment unless they re-offend
OL,18,Fwithin two years.
