OL,7,FThey avoided the maximum penalty for
OL,8,Fbreaking Health and Safety Law, which
OL,9,Fis an unlimited fine.
OL,11,FLe Sauteur told ITV News: "We will be
OL,12,Flodging an appeal in the next week or
OL,13,Fso to overturn this decision.
