OL,3,CFamily of Jersey man who died in care
OL,4,Cof paramedics who broke the law speak
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"The public support has been fantastic
OL,8,Fand a total gamechanger. As far as
OL,9,FJohn and I are concerned, the court
OL,10,Fand the Jurats are entitled to their
OL,11,Fopinion but we're public servants and
OL,12,Fthe public's opinion matters to us,
OL,13,Ftheir verdict appears to be pretty
OL,14,Funanimous."
OL,16,FA fundraiser set up to support the
OL,17,Fmedics has raised more than #47,000,
OL,18,Fhowever it has brought their access to
OL,19,Flegal aid into question.
