OL,4,Cof paramedics who broke the law speak
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FLe Sauteur explained: "We are meeting
OL,8,Fthe young lady who set up the
OL,9,Fcrowdfunding page on Wednesday. Both
OL,10,FJohn and I are committed though that,
OL,11,Fno matter what happens, we won't be
OL,12,Ffinancially gaining from this at all.
OL,14,F"We'll have to wait and see where we
OL,15,Fare with funding from legal aid, we'll
OL,16,Fhave to watch this space but we are
OL,17,Fcommitted to appeal and will have to
OL,18,Fdo whatever we can to make that
OL,19,Fhappen."
